high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the edge of the dresser where the disc lay.
Pick up the disk from under the golden statue.
Turn around over to the large black shelf with the digital alarm clock on it.
Place the disc on the shelf to the left of the digital alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Place a disc on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to face the left side of the long black dresser.
Pick up the CD from the dresser.
Bring the CD to the black shelf with the clock.
Put the CD down on the shelf next to the clock.
anns.task_desc: Put the CD down on the shelf next to the clock.

high_descs: Turn right and move toward the boots on the ground then turn right and face the dresser.
Pick up the CD that is underneath the gold toy dog on the dresser.
Turn around and move towards the window and then turn right and face the bookshelf.
Place the CD between the two pens on the bookshelf and to the left of the keys.
anns.task_desc: Place a CD on a bookshelf.
